Class NBAWarriorsShopPageStepDefinition

java.lang.Object
com.veeva.generic.keywords.GenericKeywords
com.veeva.application.stepDefinition.NBAWarriorsShopPageStepDefinition
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.veeva.generic.keywords.NonSeleniumKeywords, com.veeva.generic.keywords.SeleniumKeywords
public class NBAWarriorsShopPageStepDefinition extends com.veeva.generic.keywords.GenericKeywords
Step definitions for Cucumber scenarios targeting the NBA Warriors Shop page. This class provides the steps to select products, navigate between windows, and collect product data.
